<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Recovery - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: #fafafa;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
        
        .email-wrapper {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header {
            padding: 60px 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .brand {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 300;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 50px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .fallback-link {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            word-break: break-all;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .security-notice {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .security-notice strong {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .info-box strong {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .account-info {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .account-info strong {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .recommendations {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .recommendations-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .recommendations-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .recommendations-list li {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .recommendations-list li::before {
            content: 'â€¢';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .footer {
            padding: 40px 50px;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                padding: 18px 32px;
                font-size: 13px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="brand">{{appName}}</div>
                <div class="tagline">Premium Networking Solutions</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content">
                <div class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</div>
                
                <h1 class="title">Account Recovery Request</h1>
                
                <p class="description">
                    We received a request to recover your {{appName}} account. This recovery process will help you regain access to your account and update your email address if needed.
                </p>
                
                <div class="cta-section">
                    <a href="{{recoveryUrl}}" class="cta-button">Start Recovery Process</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="fallback-link">{{recoveryUrl}}</div>
                
                <div class="account-info">
                    <strong>Account Information:</strong><br>
                    Original Email: {{originalEmail}}<br>
                    Recovery Email: This email address
                </div>
                
                <div class="security-notice">
                    <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This recovery link expires in 30 minutes for your protection. Only use this link if you initiated the account recovery process.
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>Didn't request this?</strong> If you didn't request account recovery, you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure and no changes will be made.
                </div>
                
                <div class="recommendations">
                    <div class="recommendations-title">Security Recommendations:</div>
                    <ul class="recommendations-list">
                        <li>Keep your recovery email up to date</li>
                        <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
                        <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
                        <li>Never share your account credentials</li>
                        <li>Use a password manager</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-text">Need assistance? <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="footer-link">Contact Support</a></div>
                <div class="footer-text">&copy; {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
